      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">FORM OF RECOMMENDATION ¶ FOR A FELLOW OF THE LINNEAN SOCIETY OF LONDON ¶ . ¶ The top of a standard form of recommendation has been pasted to the top of the MS sheet, and the Linnean Society coat of ar...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">85.01.00a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To the Linnean Society of London</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Linnean Society, London, Certificates of Fellows, Foreign Members and Associates 1883-6.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; "/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3347in; text-indent: -0.3347in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>M autograph manuscript and signature; other supporters'<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>individual signatures.</p>
               </note>
               <seg rend="formtext" style="color: #2F5496; ">FORM OF RECOMMENDATION</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="formtext" style="color: #2F5496; ">FOR A FELLOW OF THE LINNEAN SOCIETY OF LONDON</seg>
               <seg rend="formtext" style="color: #2F5496; ">.</seg>
               <seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3347in; text-indent: -0.3347in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The top of a standard form of recommendation has been pasted to the top of the MS sheet, and the Linnean Society coat of arms is pasted to the left of the signatures, both cut from a printed certificate.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">We the undersigned beg to propose:</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Charles French<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3347in; text-indent: -0.3347in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Charles French<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Snr.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Name underlined in crayon.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Esqr. of Melbourne</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">for the Fellowship of the Linnean Society, to which he is well entitled by<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>his zealous working in Australian Entomology and Botany. Mr French is Secretary of the Field Naturalists Club of Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Ferd von Mueller, M.D. FLS.,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">William Woolls Ph.D., F.L.S</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Robt<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>D Fitzgerald F.L.S.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Frans. P. Pascoe<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Mr French has also English referees, thus Mr. Wallace and Mr Pascoe<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn3" n="4">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3347in; text-indent: -0.3347in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>M wrote the final paragraph at the bottom of the sheet.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>The entomologist Francis Pascoe presumably signed after the letter was received at the Society.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     </p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3347in; text-indent: -0.3347in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Annotated</seg>
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">front</seg>: This certificate was read at a General Meeting of the Society 19 March 1885 The Ballot will take place on 16th April 1885 BDJ<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>[B. D.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Jackson].</p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3347in; text-indent: -0.3347in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">back</seg>: Chas French elected 16 April 1885.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     </p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3347in; text-indent: -0.3347in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The file includes the undated obligation form signed by French, undertaking to pay the fees while he remained a member.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
         </div>
      </body>
